      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This car is in poor condition and will need some dedicated TLC and mechanical attention to get it back to its best, but it offers a great entry point for someone looking for a value-priced vehicle! It's an honest fixer-upper with plenty of potential for the right owner who isn't afraid of a little work.",
